      "role": "user",
      "content": "but i dont even watch commercials for it... i haven't even been in a store near them lately. and the logo is so crisp, like it's part of the dream, not just a blurry memory. it feels way too intentional to be a coincidence. like they're actually trying to reach me. don't you think that's weird?",
