      "content": "It's possible that subliminal marketing or incidental exposure to the brand through social media, online content, or advertising has created a lasting impression on your subconscious. Even brief exposure to the logo or branding can become deeply ingrained in your brain, leading to vivid dreams. It's not uncommon for people to experience intense dreams about brands without direct memory of encountering them recently. This phenomenon suggests that the power of perception and advertising can be more profound than you think.",
