      "content": "it's more than just perception though. it feels invasive. like, how can a company have enough influence to bypass my actual consciousness and get into my sleep? if they are using some kind of tech or frequency to target people's subconcious like that, it's actually terrifying. it's like they're colonizing our heads.",
